short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export some helpful Quicken Classic scheduled transactions data from their WebApp. This will download to a CSV file

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quicken Classic allows scheduled transaction but no ability to export these to a CSV file. This is in no way affiliated with Quicken or Intuit.  Just a 3rd party tool to get some data from their site. If you go to the Bills and Income page on the quicken classic web app (https://app.quicken.com/bills-and-income) the extension will allow you to very quickly export the main details of your scheduled transactions.  This of course requires you to be syncing to get what you have scheduled from the desktop app.  I hope it is helpful!!  -Shirezak!
